Class Appointment

  • Object
    • Appointment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Appointment>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FollowUpAppointment, ReferralAppointment

    public class Appointment
extends Object
implements Comparable<Appointment>
    Stores a normal appointment detailed information. This class is also a base class for FollowUpAppointment and ReferralAppointment class.
    Author:
    Edwin Candinegara
